like a baby?</b>

225
00:16:09,467 --> 00:16:13,137
<b>This is why I don't acknowledge you
as a fellow doctor.</b>

226
00:16:13,137 --> 00:16:16,477
<b>Instead of overcoming
such incidents, you keep whining.</b>

227
00:16:16,946 --> 00:16:20,077
