your feelings. You're not a doctor.</b>

228
00:16:30,457 --> 00:16:31,696
<b>Which unit are you going to?</b>

229
00:16:31,696 --> 00:16:33,727
<b>We're going to Unit 701.</b>

230
00:16:35,566 --> 00:16:36,967
<b>I was informed you were coming.</b>

231
00:16:36,967 --> 00:16:38,436
