294
00:19:53,426 --> 00:19:55,496
<b>Of course, I ought to help you out.</b>

295
00:19:55,767 --> 00:19:56,867
<b>I'm the best, right?</b>

296
00:19:57,367 --> 00:19:59,367
<b>Yes. Thank you.</b>

297
00:19:59,767 --> 00:20:01,867
