306
00:20:23,456 --> 00:20:24,857
<b>You can't say anything later.</b>

307
00:20:24,857 --> 00:20:26,827
<b>Okay, I got it.</b>

308
00:20:27,297 --> 00:20:29,527
<b>And as for the house,
