341
00:22:54,736 --> 00:22:56,047
<b>How are you feeling?</b>

342
00:22:57,047 --> 00:22:58,817
<b>Fine. I'm okay.</b>

343
00:23:00,476 --> 00:23:01,476
<b>I'm glad to hear that.</b>

344
00:23:01,887 --> 00:23:06,387
<b>My gosh. I can feel your affection
toward him in your voice.</b>

345
00:23:06,387 --> 00:23:08,557
<b>Are you that happy
