398
00:26:13,706 --> 00:26:15,847
<b>Well, he was there just now.</b>

399
00:26:16,476 --> 00:26:18,676
<b>I'll call him. Thank you.</b>

400
00:26:30,787 --> 00:26:32,996
<b>He even left his phone here.
