00:30:10,377 --> 00:30:12,006
<b>Are you nervous
because it has been too long?</b>

424
00:30:12,006 --> 00:30:14,017
<b>Me? No way.</b>

425
00:30:14,017 --> 00:30:16,186
<b>I think you're the one
who's nervous.</b>

426
00:30:16,186 --> 00:30:18,317
<b>If you can throw jokes,
